745
00:46:59,416 --> 00:47:01,213
Créeme.

746
00:47:01,351 --> 00:47:04,616
¿Qué tal tu música?

747
00:47:04,755 --> 00:47:05,722
No lo sé.

748
00:47:05,856 --> 00:47:07,881
